<p>I have the bellow query and it works. I just need to add a line at the bottom that gives the grand total </p>  <pre><code>SELECT ItemType.Description,         SUM(Price * Quantity)as 'TOTAL' FROM [MIETRAK].[dbo].[PurchaseOrderReceivingLine] join Item    on PurchaseOrderReceivingLine.ItemFK = item.ItemPK join ItemType    on Item.ItemTypeFK = ItemType.ItemTypePK join PurchaseOrderReceiving    on PurchaseOrderReceivingLine.PurchaseOrderReceivingFK = PurchaseOrderReceiving.PurchaseOrderReceivingPK where InvoiceDate &gt;=  dateadd(wk, datediff(wk, 0, getdate()) - 1, 0)     and InvoiceDate &lt; dateadd(wk, datediff(wk, 0, getdate()), 0) group by ItemType.Description </code></pre>